    {
      "id": "task_1756888903884_r006apt8j",
      "title": "Implement Nexus Copilot - Comprehensive API Integration",
      "description": "Build a powerful Nexus copilot system that integrates with ALL API features in the Sim codebase. This will create a self-powered AI assistant using Claude API that can interact with workflows, users, billing, knowledge bases, templates, and all other system components.\n\nCOMPREHENSIVE INTEGRATION SCOPE:\n\n1. NEXUS TOOLSET CREATION:\n- Create apps/sim/lib/nexus/tools/ directory\n- Implement comprehensive tools for ALL major API endpoints:\n  * Workflow management (create, read, update, delete, execute)\n  * User management and authentication\n  * Billing and subscription management\n  * Knowledge base operations\n  * Template management and deployment\n  * File operations (upload, download, organize)\n  * OAuth credential management\n  * Organization and team management\n  * Environment variable management\n  * Usage tracking and analytics\n  * Webhook management\n  * Custom tool integration\n\n2. NEXUS BACKEND API:\n- Create apps/sim/app/api/nexus/chat/route.ts\n- Implement streaming Claude 3.5 Sonnet integration\n- Connect all Nexus tools with proper error handling\n- Add comprehensive logging and monitoring\n\n3. NEXUS FRONTEND INTEGRATION:\n- Duplicate and enhance copilot UI components\n- Create dedicated Nexus panel in workflow editor\n- Implement rich UI for tool responses\n- Add visual feedback for complex operations\n\n4. TOOL IMPLEMENTATION REQUIREMENTS:\n- Each tool must have comprehensive error handling\n- All tools should include detailed logging\n- Implement proper authentication and authorization\n- Add input validation and sanitization\n- Include comprehensive JSDoc documentation\n\n5. ADVANCED FEATURES:\n- Multi-step workflow automation\n- Contextual awareness of current workspace/workflow\n- Intelligent suggestions based on user activity\n- Integration with existing Sim copilot for coordination\n\nSUCCESS CRITERIA:\n- Nexus can perform ALL major operations available via Sim APIs\n- Complete integration with authentication and authorization\n- Comprehensive error handling and user feedback\n- Production-ready code with full logging and monitoring\n- Seamless UI integration with existing workflow editor",
      "mode": "DEVELOPMENT",
      "category": "missing-feature",
      "priority": "high",
      "status": "in_progress",
      "dependencies": [],
      "important_files": [
        "/apps/sim/app/api",
        "/apps/sim/lib",
        "/apps/sim/app/workspace/[workspaceId]/w/[workflowId]/components/panel"
      ],
      "success_criteria": [
        "Nexus copilot successfully integrated into workflow editor",
        "All major API endpoints accessible via Nexus tools",
        "Comprehensive error handling and logging implemented",
        "Production-ready code with full documentation"
      ],
